    "Deeper engagement and much more argument is required to defend the Anscombean picture of cognitive agency set out above.",
    "This is a job for future studies.",
    "To conclude for now, I'll condense the argument as it has proceeded section by section before stepping back and appraising the result so far.",
    "In (§2) I presented a general framework for understanding cognition, suggesting that we have good philosophical reasons to understand cognition as normatively constrained information processing in the service of certain salient goals.",
    "In (§3) I suggested that cognitive offloading allows environmental resources to be incorporated into systems structured in this kind of way."
